-> JAXB stands for Java Architecture for XML binding
-> JAXB api is used to convert java object to XML and vice versa
Converting java object to XML is known as---> Marshalling.
Converting of XML into java object is --> UnMarshalling.
***************************************************************************
Steps for marshalling or unmarshalling

Step1:- create binding class(java bean based class)
step2:- define mapping betweem java programming elements to XML.
(the mapping we can define by using JAXB annotation)
step3:- write logic for marshalling or unmarshalling as per requirement
 